Hi, I’m Andre and it is my pleasure to serve you.  My team has one of the highest ratings on Turo because we do more than rent cars…we anticipate the needs of our clients while providing the literal vehicle to your exceptional experience in Atlanta.  From the moment that you secure your reservation to the moment that you return the keys, your satisfaction is our top priority.  

Are you in town to see the Falcons or United FC?  Try our Range Rover Sport,  Porsche Boxster or Mercedes Benz G Class. Either can be the perfect vehicle to carry you from tailgate to after-party and everywhere in between. You may be attending alone or you may travel with a group of friends…just remember, no matter who you are traveling with, how you arrive matters!.

Perhaps, you are more interested in sealing the business deal of the decade.  Take a look at our Bentley Continental or the Jaguar XJ.  Meeting your boss or chauffeuring your new client around town in one of these vehicles breeds confidence in your ability. Your ride says success, success says competence, competence gets you the new job or promotion!

Maybe you have finally found the time for the nice family vacation you’ve been putting off.  Well, load up the spouse and kids in the Escalade.  Plenty of room for the little ones to stretch their legs while keeping with the luxury that you are accustomed to.  Maybe gas mileage is the driving factor, then the Lexus IS may be exactly what you need...providing economical travel without skimping on style. Whatever you decide, we count it a privilege to take a small part in making your family memories.

Regardless to why you have chosen the great city of Atlanta, our fleet is sure to have the perfect vehicle for you.   We have a variety of luxury vehicles to suit all tastes, and we have a passion for providing the type of service that exceeds expectations. Questions and concerns will be addressed in a timely manner. All vehicles will be professionally detailed and sanitized to meet current health regulations, even providing you with a mask for your personal safety.  Your vehicle will be delivered to the agreed upon location prior to scheduled time.  Our team understands that if we aren’t early, then we’re late, and lateness does not keep us as an All-Star Host.  

Atlanta is home….a city that we love.  If my team and I are allowed to provide you with a vehicle to experience it, if only for a short time, we will count it as an honor. We look forward to serving you.

Hey There! My name is Tia Mays, I am a Midwest girl living the Southern life. I moved to Atlanta when I was working for a well known car rental line. I knew within the first year (spent 5 total), that I wanted to eventually have my own fleet line of cars! So I’m here to get started with my dream. I love being in the car, rather is driving the 14 hours back home, or taking weekend get away, I enjoy driving. I have rented my fair share of cars professionally and as a consumer! I want my customers to feel like family when they are done with their rental, I want it to be easy and stress free! 

As a mother I have gotten to learn the art of patience, and understanding, these are both things that are very important in renting cars. 

More about me!!! I work in IT sales and absolutely love it, my spare time consist of playing basketball, watching football, cooking, spending time with my son, and traveling! 

I hope to share an amazing experience with you!

Follow us on Instagram @pureexoticsatl

Hi. Dear friend! Nice to meet you on Turo!

As a new immigrant, a single dad of two little girls(8 & 2), im also a full-time Turo host/co-host.

Although my English proficiency is limited, I believe that through our communication and your experience with our car, you will see that I am friendly, sincere, responsible, and someone who values cleanliness.

Turo is currently my only occupation and the main source of income for my family. Therefore, we place the utmost importance on our work with Turo, your satisfaction with our service, and the maintenance of our vehicles. I am confident that you will be pleased and reassured by choosing our car for your journey.

The Turo platform represents a new beginning for me, and it is also a challenge for a new immigrant with a language barrier. I will continuously learn and improve through this process, striving to provide an exceptional service experience for every trip. If you have any suggestions or feedback during your journey, please feel free to share them. We will gladly consider or adopt them.

Thank you for taking the time to read this. We look forward to seeing you on your trip!🤝
